&lt;h1 class="relative group">What is the Reality
&lt;div id="what-is-the-reality" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#what-is-the-reality" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>You see something on a table and you ask yourself, &amp;ldquo;What is that?&amp;rdquo; &lt;br>
Answer: It looks like an apple, so it is an apple. &lt;br>
Then you ask, &amp;ldquo;How many apples are there?&amp;rdquo; &lt;br>
Answer: You know the counting, and after counting, you say it is three.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>It&amp;rsquo;s a very simple process, isn&amp;rsquo;t it? &lt;br>
You know the truth after asking these two questions.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>